  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型的工作日流程。整体分成两大块：上班和回家。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "section Go to work",
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个section。上班那段具体有哪些步骤？每个步骤需要标注满意度分数和参与角色吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "score",
        "actor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "上班部分：先泡茶，这个我很享受，打5分；然后上楼去书房，3分；接着工作本身比较痛苦，只有1分，而且我家猫会过来打扰，所以参与者要加上Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea: 5: Me",
        "Go upstairs: 3: Me",
        "Do work: 1: Me, Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，上班部分三步：泡茶5分、上楼3分、工作1分（你和猫）。那回家section呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "回家就简单了：下楼5分，终于解脱了；然后坐下来休息3分。都是我自己。对了，整个图标题就叫\"My working day\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title My working day",
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me",
        "Sit down: 3: Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，你看看：两个section，上班三步、回家两步，分数和角色都标上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey diagram"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，工作那步的参与者，我刚才说错了——不是Cat，应该是Cat和我，但写法上是不是该写成\"Me, Cat\"？还有，下楼那步我想改成5分，回家心情更好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Do work: 1: Me, Cat",
        "Go downstairs: 5: Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正：工作步骤参与者改为\"Me, Cat\"，下楼分数调到5分。现在结构和数据都对了。",
